snippet.title: Game & Watch - Flagman (c)1980 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: 2nd ever Game and Watch.  Nintendo's take on 'Simon'  Support for this will be in MAME 0.214, thanks to algestam for the emulation and hydef for the artwork.  Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5
